    <p>
      Charging tariffs for electric vehicles (EVs) in Germany.
      <br>
      <abbr title="Alternating Current">AC</abbr> and <abbr title="Direct Current">DC</abbr> prices are: <code>&euro; /
      <abbr title="Kilowatt-hour">kWh</abbr></code>.
      <br>
      For most providers, <abbr title="Direct Current">DC</abbr> slow is <code>&le; 50 <abbr title="Kilowatt">kW</abbr></code> and <abbr title="Direct Current">DC</abbr> fast is <code>&gt; 50 <abbr title="Kilowatt">kW</abbr></code>.
      <br>
      Tesla Supercharger prices can vary.
    </p>

